WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:08.500
Story: An Unusual Tuesday

2
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.500
It was Tuesday,

3
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.500
and I went to a wedding.

4
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
There was a groom and a bride,

5
00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:25.500
and many guests.

6
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.500
But the groom and the bride were arguing.

7
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:41.500
The guests were surprised.

8
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.500
When the party was over,

9
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:51.500
we went to watch a play.

10
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:58.500
In the play, there was a magician.

11
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.800
The magician said,

12
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:08.500
"I won't be a puppet in your hands."

13
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.500
All the people laughed.

14
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:18.500
After that, I saw a pilot

15
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:23.500
sitting with his friends.

16
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
Talk to us a little bit

17
00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:32.500
about corruption in the state.

18
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:37.500
I was speaking slowly,

19
00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:45.500
meaning I was speaking at a relaxed pace.

20
00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:51.500
But after a while,

21
00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:57.500
I was able to speak quickly.

22
00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:01.500
After that, we went to look at

23
00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.500
the Hindu temple.

24
00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:13.500
And we went home on Thursday.

25
00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:20.000
And that was the end of the week.